**Add these new functions:**

1. `convertInputs(req *model.LLMRequest) ([]inputItem, string)` â€” converts ADK Contents to Responses API input items. Extracts system instruction as separate `instructions` string. Maps `FunctionCall` parts to `{type: "function_call", call_id, name, arguments}` items. Maps `FunctionResponse` parts to `{type: "function_call_output", call_id, output}` items. Maps text parts to `{type: "message", role, content}` items.

2. `convertResponseTools(req *model.LLMRequest, wsConfig *WebSearch) []responseTool` â€” converts ADK tools to Responses API flat format. Function tools become `{type: "function", name, description, parameters}` (flat, NOT nested in a `function` key). If GoogleSearch marker is present, adds `{type: "web_search", search_context_size, filters}` using wsConfig.

3. `convertResponseOutput(resp *responsesResponse) *model.LLMResponse` â€” converts Responses API output items to ADK LLMResponse. Maps `function_call` items to `genai.FunctionCall` parts (use `call_id` as the ID). Maps `message` items' text content to text parts. Skips `web_search_call` items. Sets usage metadata.

